text: eemaanadaaron mein se kuchh log aise bhee hain ki khuda se unhonne (jonisaaree ka) jo ehad kiya tha use poora kar dikhaaya garaz unamen se baaz vah hain jo (mar kar) apana vakt poora kar gae aur unamen se baaz (hukme khuda ke) muntazir baithe hain aur un logon ne (apanee baat) zara bhee nahin badalee
